Snakeskin is used in the Crafting skill to make snakeskin armour. It can be created by giving a snake hide or swamp snake hide and a small fee of coins to a tanner, the specific amount depending on the type of hide and the particular tanner. Tanners can be found in Al-Kharid, Canifis, the Ranging Guild, the Crafting Guild, and the Forthos Dungeon.

'''Snakeskin''' is used in the [[Crafting]] skill to make [[snakeskin armour]]. It can be created by giving a [[snake hide]] or [[Snake hide (swamp)|swamp snake hide]] and a small fee of [[coins]] to a [[tanner]], the specific amount depending on the type of hide and the particular tanner. Tanners can be found in [[Al-Kharid]], [[Canifis]], the [[Ranging Guild]], the [[Crafting Guild]], and the [[Forthos Dungeon]].
